str2: No, not. Also ouk, and ouch a primary word; the absolute negative adverb; no or not.
Adam, the first man, the first parent of the human race. Of Hebrew origin; Adam, the first man; typically man.

str2: To deceive, cheat, lead into error. Of uncertain derivation; to cheat, i.e. Delude.

The, the definite article. Including the feminine he, and the neuter to in all their inflections; the definite article; the.
A woman, wife, my lady. Probably from the base of ginomai; a woman; specially, a wife.
